This paper discusses the design and deployment of wireless networks, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of network infrastructure densification and network-wise coordination, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and system control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of mobile user devices, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and augmented reality (cs.AR).
